description:
Danique, who is one of our LED Live hosts and content creators, was addicted to YouTube for years. Watch to see how God helped her overcome by reminding her of Jesus' soon return, and how wasting her time wasn't an option anymore if she wanted a real relationship with Jesus. This is a must watch!
